milestones.description: Peter Kirsten and Richardson's 79-run partnership is SA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Wessels and Adrian Kuiper
Peter Kirsten and McMillan's 41-run partnership is SA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Richard Snell and McMillan
Richard Snell and McMillan's 28-run partnership is SA's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Richardson and Richard Snell
Allan Donald has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for SA, going past Peter Kirsten
